Package FOMS.menu_manager

Class Burger

  • java.lang.Object
    • FOMS.menu_manager.MenuItem
      • FOMS.menu_manager.Burger
  • public class Burger
extends MenuItem
    A class representing a burger item in the menu. Inherits from the MenuItem class. The Burger class provides constructors to create burger items with different parameters. It inherits attributes and methods from the MenuItem class.
